@startuml forgotpwd_sequence_simplified
title Forgot Password - Interface to Entity Sequence

actor User
boundary "Forgot Password Interface" as ForgotPWDInterface
control ForgotPWDController
entity UserRepository
entity UserEntity

User -> ForgotPWDInterface: Enter email and submit
ForgotPWDInterface -> ForgotPWDController: POST /forgotpwd (email)
ForgotPWDController -> UserRepository: findOneBy(email)
UserRepository -> UserEntity: load user data
UserEntity --> UserRepository: user/null
UserRepository --> ForgotPWDController: user/null

alt User exists
    ForgotPWDController -> UserEntity: setResetToken(token, expiresAt)
    UserEntity --> ForgotPWDController: token assigned
    ForgotPWDController --> ForgotPWDInterface: Success message
else User not found
    ForgotPWDController --> ForgotPWDInterface: Error message
end

@enduml